commit.message:
Fixed deprecations and simplified how output paths are obtained
Base IDEA version now is 2022.2
When saving modified class files, ask whether to overwrite the original class fies or to save to a different output directory with the option to remember the selection
Support reading class files compiled by Java 19 and Java 20
Fix "class root not found" message in IntelliJ IDEA plugin
Attaching in development mode did not work anymore
Fixed accidental changes to installer configuration
